        {"ID":"campaign_chalicedivers","Entry":"地牢潜兵"},
        {"ID":"campaign_chalicedivers_tooltip","Entry":"A limited-scope campaign aimed at learning or experimenting with combat systems. Death no longer result in a game over.\nStart the campaign with up to 2 additional companions chosen from a preset selection (Starting Option Companion is disabled in this campaign)\nLimit: Player Character Origin must be Forest Dweller\nStarting Gift Companion is disabled.\n\nThis is a parody of Bloodborne, with some more references from various ero-games."},
